text: "Intentions" is a song by Canadian singer Justin Bieber featuring rapper and Migos member Quavo. It was released on February 7, 2020, as the second single from Bieber's fifth studio album Changes. The song peaked at number five on the Billboard Hot 100. ==References== Category:Pop songs Category:Rap songs Category:2020 songs Category:Justin Bieber songs
title: Intentions (Justin Bieber song)
